name: Intermittent 30/15's #2
description:
After warming up, the session will focus on completing a series of intermittent style intervals. This type of training is ideal for maximizing adaptations to Max Aerobic fitness. 



Intermittent intervals allow you to complete a more significant amount of work at your Max Aerobic intensity than continuous intervals would allow. 



The main set consists of completing 8 x 30/15's.
